N = 9 + \underbrace{99}_2 +\underbrace{999}_3 + ... + \underbrace{999 ... 99}_{999}
\displaystyle N = \sum_{k=1}^{999} (10^k - 1) = \dfrac{10(10^{999}-1)}{9} - 999 
N = 9 + 99 + 999 + ... = 
(10 - 1) + (100 - 1) + (1000 - 1)+ ... =
(10 + 100 + 1000 + ...) - 999 = 
111...1110 - 999 = 
111...10111
\rm\phantom{\ 10\ S -} S\  =\ \ 9\cdots 9\ +\ \cdots\ +\ 999\ +\ 99\ +\ 9
\rm\ 10\ S - S\ =\ \ 9\cdots 90\ +\ \cdots +\ (990-999)\ +\ (90-99)\ -\ 9  
\rm\quad \Rightarrow\ \  9\ S\ =\ \ \: 9\cdots90\  +\ 999\ (-9)
\rm\quad \Rightarrow\quad\ \ S\ =\ \ 1\cdots10\ - \ 999
